import React from 'react'
import { WhitePortfolioContainer, RedHeaderBox } from '../lib/container'
import { BoxHeader, BoxText } from '../lib/text'

export const TechSection = () => {
  return (
    <WhitePortfolioContainer>
      <RedHeaderBox>
        <BoxHeader>TECH</BoxHeader>
      </RedHeaderBox>
      <BoxText>
        JavaScript, React, Redux, CSS, HTML, Node.js, MongoDB, React Native, Git
      </BoxText>
    </WhitePortfolioContainer>
  )
}

export default TechSection
